🧭 Step 6: Sidebar Navigation (LIKE IDE 🔥)

📄 Update MainFrame.java

Replace simple tab UI with:

JSplitPane mainSplit = new JSplitPane();

String[] menuItems = {"Snippets", "API Tester", "Logs"};

JList<String> sidebar = new JList<>(menuItems);
sidebar.setSelectionMode(ListSelectionModel.SINGLE_SELECTION);

JPanel contentPanel = new JPanel(new CardLayout());

SnippetPanel snippetPanel = new SnippetPanel();
contentPanel.add(snippetPanel, "Snippets");

sidebar.addListSelectionListener(e -> {
    CardLayout cl = (CardLayout) contentPanel.getLayout();
    cl.show(contentPanel, sidebar.getSelectedValue());
});

mainSplit.setLeftComponent(new JScrollPane(sidebar));
mainSplit.setRightComponent(contentPanel);

mainSplit.setDividerLocation(150);

add(mainSplit);


